    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so logical, you know? like, why keep fighting a battle that's already over. every time i try to pull myself up, the exhaustion just brings me right back down. like there's nothing waiting for me on the other side of this besides more of the same. it's like i'm just running on empty and there's no way to refill it. everything just feels so final.",
